                     <interp inst="t17871024-21-verdict116" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing, but not privately
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17871024-21-punish117" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17871024-21-punish117" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871024-21-defend244 t17871024-21-punish117"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
